---
title: Garden Ranch Chicken with Cauliflower “Rice” Fritters, Zucchini & Creamy Mushroom Sauce
description: This low carb dinner feels indulgent and has all the textures and flavor you crave! Here’s the deal: Ranch-spiced chicken, perfectly cooked, then topped with a creamy, tomato-based sauce with a side of sauteed zucchini. The clincher is a cauliflower “rice” and scallion fritter, bound together with a smidge of flour, crisp-fried and ready for crunching–while keeping you off that carb train.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/garden-ranch-chicken-e5235a28.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/garden-ranch-chicken-636130f567bef9fa8d0f85f6-5a0b086e.pdf
time required: 40 minutes
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/garden-ranch-chicken-636130f567bef9fa8d0f85f6
course: main course
servings: 2
author: HelloFresh
cuisine: North America
nutrition:
  calories: 520 kcal
